description.en:
AngelHeart is a tech ecosystem with multiple independent projects aiming at rewarding token holders.

AngelHeart’s Ecosystem includes: 

4 tech projects including:
•	Cryptoedge: CryptoEdge is the first project in the AngelHeart ecosystem. It will power the revolutionary CryptoEdge platform which will feature state of the art analytic tools for cryptocurrencies & stocks as well as a cryptoswap & an NFT marketplace.

•	WebsitesIQ: WebsitesIQ is the second project in the AngelHeart ecosystem. It is our independent tech project. With websitesIQ, you can quickly create a website or a mobile app as well as in-depth tutorials on web and app development.


•	DesignsIQ:  DesignsIQ is the third project in the AngelHeart ecosystem. It helps create the best logos, social media presentations, youtube thumbnails, banners, posters & cards to take your social media presence or your business to the next level!

•	Varoo3D: Varoo3D is the fourth project in the AngelHeart ecosystem. Varoo3D is a 3D model generator for social media avatars, a 3D model viewer for businesses and ecommerce, as well as valuable 3D resources for artists.
